This is a great app by helpful and responsive developers.  Based on my toddlers reaction to this game it is a hit.  Using simple touch controls you can customise your monster as you navigate around a fantastical landscape. Both above and below water there are lots of neat interactive elements to enjoy.  Controls are simple but intuitive and have already provided hours of enjoyment for my son.  Well thought out and will implemented.
Thank you!
